abstract: I buried my secret as deep as I could.  I never spoke of it, I never cross dressed, I tried so hard to be him.

headline_main: Transgender Lives: Your Stories: Theresa Fisher

abstract: As imperfect as the world is today, as hard as it is to be transgender and live an authentic life, it was much worse, not so long ago.
